@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ahmucq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.81 + v1 + 0.15) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.01)) - wp.cos(0.69))
    v1 = v2
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs(0.99))
    v1 = wp.abs(tmp)
    tmp = wp.abs((0.73 - (v1 + 0.29 + v1 + 0.68)))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.79) / 0.93)
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.78) / ((tmp + 0.99 * v1 + 0.99) * v0))
    data[tid] = v0
